                Thanks for joining <strong><%= appName || 'MyApp' %></strong>. Weâ€™re excited to have you on board.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 22px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7; color:#334155;">
                Your account has been created. You can jump right in and explore your dashboard.
              </p>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin: 0 0 18px;">
                <tr>
                  <td bgcolor="<%= brandColor || '#4e73df' %>" style="border-radius:10px; text-align:center;">
                    <a href="<%= ctaUrl || (baseUrl ? baseUrl + '/dashboard' : '#') %>"
                       class="button"
                       style="display:inline-block; padding:12px 20px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; color:#ffffff; background:<%= brandColor || '#4e73df' %>; border-radius:10px;">
                      Go to Dashboard
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-size:13px; color:#64748b;">
                If the button doesnâ€™t work, paste this link into your browser:
              </p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 22px; font-size:13px;">
                <a class="link" href="<%= ctaUrl || (baseUrl ? baseUrl + '/dashboard' : '#') %>" style="color:<%= brandColor || '#4e73df' %>;">
                  <%= ctaUrl || (baseUrl ? baseUrl + '/dashboard' : '#') %>
                </a>
              </p>

              <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 14px 0 18px;">

              <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#64748b;">
                Need help? <a class="link" href="<%= helpUrl || 'mailto:support@yourdomain.tld' %>" style="color:<%= brandColor || '#4e73df' %>;">Contact support</a>.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
